<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Liens_externes">Liens externes</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Orhan_Pamuk&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=27" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Liens externes">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Orhan_Pamuk&amp;action=edit&amp;section=27" title="Modifier la section : Liens externes">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li><abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : anglais">(en)</abbr>/<abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : turc">(tr)</abbr> <cite class="ouvrage" id="site_officiel" style="font-style: normal;"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.orhanpamuk.net/">Site officiel</a></cite></li>
