"><i>Hrvatska Enciklopedija</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ne.se/uppslagsverk/encyklopedi/lång/orhan-pamuk"><i>Swedish Nationalencyklopedin</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.munzinger.de/search/go/document.jsp?id=00000022898">Munzinger Archiv</a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://snl.no/Orhan_Pamuk"><i>Store norske leksikon</i></a></li>
